<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">

<head>
    <title>Mon compte</title>
    <link href="/bs/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>

<body>
    <%- include("Navbar.component.ejs",{ page: "Mon compte" }) %>
            <div class="container">

                <% if(success.length > 0) { %>
                    <div class="alert alert-dismissible alert-success">
                        <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="alert">&times;</button>
                        <%= success %>
                    </div>
                <% } %>

                <span class="h4">Informations du compte</span>  
                <ul class="mt-3" >     
                    <li>
                        Pseudo : <% if(typeof(pseudo) !== "undefined") {%>
                            <%= pseudo%>
                            <%}%>
                    </li>   
                    <li>
                        Pseudo Twitter : <% if(typeof(pseudo_twitter) !== "undefined") {%>
                            <%= pseudo_twitter%>
                            <%} else { %>
                              <strong>Aucun compte Twitter associé</strong>  
                            <%}%>
                    </li>     
                    <li>
                        Email : <% if(typeof(email) !== "undefined") {%>
                            <%= email %>
                            <%}%>
                    </li>     
                </ul>
                <a href="/modifier-mon-compte" class="btn btn-outline-secondary">Mettre à jour le profil</a>
                <button class="btn btn-danger d-block my-3" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#modalDelete">Supprimer le compte</button>
                </div>
                
                <div class="modal fade" id="modalDelete" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="modalAction" aria-hidden="true">
                    <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered" role="document">
                        <div class="modal-content">
                        <div class="modal-header bg-danger">
                            <h5 class="modal-title text-white font-weight-bold" id="modalTitle">Suppression du compte</h5>
                            <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
                            <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
                            </button>
                        </div>
                        <div class="modal-body">
                            
                                <p>Vous vous apprêtez à supprimer votre compte utilisateur.<br/><strong>Cette action est irréversible.</strong></p>
                                <p>Vous ne pourrez plus consulter vos tweets ni accéder <strong>dashboard</strong>.</p>
                                <p class="font-weight-bold text-danger">Le confirmez-vous ?</p>
        
                        </div>
                        <div class="modal-footer">
                            <a href="/delete-account" class="btn btn-danger">Confirmer</a>
                            <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-dismiss="modal">Fermer</button>
                        </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
            </div>

            <script src="/js/jquery.min.js"></script>
            <script src="/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>

</html>